OL,3,CHome Secretary plans visa bans for
OL,4,Cthree countries amid asylum system
OL,5,Coverhaul
OL,7,FShabana Mahmood will ban three
OL,8,Fcountries from accessing UK visas if
OL,9,Fthey fail to take back illegal
OL,10,Fmigrants as she plans to overhaul
OL,11,Fhuman rights law as part of a sweeping
OL,12,Freform of the asylum system.
OL,14,FThree African countries, Angola,
OL,15,FNamibia and the Democratic Republic of
OL,16,FCongo, will face visa sanctions,
OL,17,Fblocking their tourists, VIPs and
OL,18,Fbusiness people from travelling to
OL,19,FBritain if they do not co-operate more
OL,20,Fon the removal of illegal migrants.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
