OL,3,CHome Secretary plans visa bans for
OL,4,Cthree countries amid asylum system
OL,5,Coverhaul
OL,7,FThe move was reportedly inspired by
OL,8,FTrump administration homeland security
OL,9,Fsecretary Kristi Noem, according to
OL,10,Fthe Times.
OL,12,FMs Mahmood said: "In Britain, we play
OL,13,Fby the rules. When I said there would
OL,14,Fbe penalties for countries that do not
OL,15,Ftake back criminals and illegal
OL,16,Fimmigrants, I meant it.
OL,18,F"My message to foreign governments
OL,19,Ftoday is clear: accept the return of
OL,20,Fyour citizens or lose the privilege of
OL,21,Fentering our country."
