OL,5,Coverhaul
OL,7,FMs Mahmood is set to rewrite how
OL,8,FBritain grants refuge to those fleeing
OL,9,Fconflict and upheaval with a statement
OL,10,Fin the House of Commons on Monday.
OL,12,FThe reforms are billed as the largest
OL,13,Fchange to the UK's asylum system in
OL,14,Fthe modern era, and have been inspired
OL,15,Fby a strict approach taken by Denmark.
OL,17,FShe will bring forward a Bill to
OL,18,Fchange how the right to family life
OL,19,Funder Article 8 of the European
OL,20,FConvention on Human Rights (ECHR) is
OL,21,Fapplied in migration court cases.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
