OL,7,FOnly those with immediate relatives,
OL,8,Flike children or parents, will be able
OL,9,Fto remain in the UK in future.
OL,11,FThe Home Secretary also plans to
OL,12,Fchange the law so that multiple
OL,13,Fattempts to appeal against refusals
OL,14,Ffor asylum will no longer be allowed.
OL,16,FMs Mahmood has insisted the overhaul
OL,17,Fis needed because the "pace and scale
OL,18,Fof change destabilised communities".
