OL,7,FOn Sunday, the Home Secretary warned
OL,8,Fpublic consent for the asylum system
OL,9,Fmay disappear if her major reforms
OL,10,Fwere not introduced.
OL,12,FMs Mahmood is also expected to fast-
OL,13,Ftrack the removal of dangerous
OL,14,Fcriminals, and to expedite hearings
OL,15,Ffor last-minute appeals against
OL,16,Fdeportation.
OL,18,FSimilarly, claims by migrants that
OL,19,Fthey are facing modern slavery will be
OL,20,Fmore closely scrutinised as a result
OL,21,Fof tweaks to the Modern Slavery Act.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
