OL,7,FOther reforms already trailed as part
OL,8,Fof the raft of reforms include that
OL,9,Frefugee status will be made temporary,
OL,10,Fso that people are returned to their
OL,11,Fhomeland once it becomes safe.
OL,13,FAt the same time, safe and legal
OL,14,Froutes to the UK will be introduced as
OL,15,Fa way to cut dangerous journeys in
OL,16,Fsmall boats across the English Channel.
OL,18,FMeanwhile, housing and weekly
OL,19,Fallowances will no longer be
OL,20,Fguaranteed for asylum seekers.
