OL,7,FAI facial age estimate technology is
OL,8,Falso being rolled out to identify
OL,9,Fmigrants' age, in a bid to find out
OL,10,Fwhether those claiming to be children
OL,11,Freally are.
OL,13,FMinisters have taken inspiration from
OL,14,Fthe strict asylum approach taken by
OL,15,Fthe Danes, whose government is of the
OL,16,Fsame political stripe as Labour and
OL,17,Fhas increased deportations of illegal
OL,18,Fmigrants.
