OL,7,FThe Government's plans have attracted
OL,8,Fsome criticism, with the Refugee
OL,9,FCouncil warning they would accrue a
OL,10,Fcost of #872 million over 10 years as
OL,11,Fa result of the need to review asylum
OL,12,Fseekers' status to remain in the UK.
OL,14,FEnver Solomon, the charity's chief
OL,15,Fexecutive, insisted the changes "will
OL,16,Fnot deter people from making dangerous
OL,17,Fcrossings, but they will unfairly
OL,18,Fprevent men, women and children from
OL,19,Fintegrating into British life".
