OL,7,FSome 39,075 people have arrived in the
OL,8,FUK after crossing the English Channel
OL,9,Fin small boats so far this year,
OL,10,Faccording to the latest Home Office
OL,11,Ffigures.
OL,13,FThe arrivals have already passed the
OL,14,Fnumber for the whole of 2024 (36,816)
OL,15,Fand 2023 (29,437) but the number is
OL,16,Fbelow the total for 2022 (45,774).
